Item: RPLidar A1M8 360 Degree Laser Scanner Development Kit
Description: RPLIDAR A1 is a low cost 360-degree 2D laser scanner (LIDAR) solution developed by SLAMTEC. The system can perform a 360degree scan within a 6meter range. The produced 2D point cloud data can be used in mapping, localization, and object/environment modeling.
9V battery but with a built in charging port
Micro DC geared motor with 120:1 ratio and encoder for precise control. Ideal for mobile robots, compatible with Arduino and Gravity interface.
5521 Converter Center Negative 9 Volt Power Supply Cable
Breadboard-Friendly 2.1mm PCB Mounting Female DC Power Barrel Jack (5 PCS DC Power Jack)
